BEAUTIFLYs favorite food is the sweet
pollen of flowers. If you want to see
this POKMON, just leave a potted flower by an open window. BEAUTIFLY
is sure to come looking for pollen.

BEAUTIFLY has a long mouth like a coiled
needle, which is very convenient for
collecting pollen from flowers. This POKMON rides the spring winds as
it flits around gathering pollen.

Its colorfully patterned wings are its
most prominent feature. It flies through
flower-covered fields collecting pollen.
It attacks ferociously when angered.

Despite its appearance, it has an
aggressive nature. It attacks by jabbing
with its long, thin mouth.

Despite its appearance, it has an
aggressive nature. It attacks by jabbing
with its long, thin mouth.

It has an aggressive nature. It
stabs prey with its long, narrow
mouth to drain the preys fluids.

When flower fields bloom, it flits

La nourriture prfre de Charmillon est le pollen sucr
des fleurs. Si on veut voir ce Pokmon, il suffit de laisser
une fleur en pot sur un rebord de fentre. Charmillon viendra
srement voir sil y a du pollen.

Papinellas Lieblingsspeise ist Bltenstaub. Wenn du dieses
Pokmon beobachten mchtest, musst du blo einen
Blumentopf vor ein geffnetes Fenster stellen. Papinella
wird sich diese Leckerei nicht entgehen lassen.

La comida favorita de Beautifly es el dulce polen de las flores.
Si quieres ver a este Pokmon, deja una maceta con flores al
lado de la ventana y vers cmo aparece un ejemplar de
Beautifly en busca de polen.

Il nutrimento preferito da Beautifly  il polline dei fiori.
Per attirare questo Pokmon basta mettere una pianta fiorita
sul davanzale: senza dubbio si avviciner in cerca di polline.
